SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Last Meas Excretion Rate Norm by SA

SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Last Measurable Excretion Rate Normalized by Surface Area

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Last Meas Excretion Rate Norm by WT
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The last measurable (positive) excretion rate divided by the weight.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Last Measurable Excretion Rate Normalized by Weight

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Max Excretion Rate
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The maximum excretion rate determined for the specimen type specified in PPSPEC.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Maximum Observed Excretion Rate

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Max Excretion Rate Norm by BMI
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The maximum excretion rate divided by the body mass index.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Maximum Observed Excretion Rate Normalized by Body Mass Index

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Max Excretion Rate Norm by Dose
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The maximum excretion rate divided by the dose.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Maximum Observed Excretion Rate Normalized by Dose

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Max Excretion Rate Norm by SA
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The maximum excretion rate divided by the surface area.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Maximum Observed Excretion Rate Normalized by Surface Area

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Max Excretion Rate Norm by WT
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The maximum excretion rate divided by the weight.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Maximum Observed Excretion Rate Normalized by Weight

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Midpoint of Interval of Last Nonzero ER
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The midpoint of collection interval associated with last measurable excretion rate.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Collection Interval Midpoint

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Midpoint of Interval of Maximum ER
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The midpoint of collection interval associated with the maximum excretion rate.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Time of Maximum Observed Excretion Rate

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Absolute Bioavailability
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The fraction of the treatment dose that reaches the systemic circulation; this is the ratio of the amount of drug in the system (area under the curve) after extravascular administration of a test formulation divided by the drug in the system (area under the curve) after IV administration.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Absolute Bioavailability

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Fraction Bound
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The percent or ratio of bound substance concentration to the total concentration.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Fraction Bound

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Fluctuation%
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The difference between Cmin and Cmax standardized to Cavg, between dose time and Tau.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Concentration Variability Between Dose Time and Tau

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Fraction of the Dose Metabolized
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The fraction of the bioavailable dose which has been metabolized.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Fraction of the Dose Metabolized

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Relative Bioavailability
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The fraction of the treatment dose that reaches the systemic circulation relative to a reference route or reference formulation. The ratio of the amount of drug in the system (area under the curve) after administration of a test formulation divided by the drug in the system after a non-IV administration of a reference formulation and/or reference route.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Relative Bioavailability

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Fract Excr from T1 to T2
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The fraction of the administered dose that is recovered from the specimen type specified in PPSPEC, over the interval between T1 and T2.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Fractional Excretion from T1 to T2

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Fraction Unbound
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The percent or ratio of free substance concentration to the total concentration. (NCI)
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Fraction Unbound

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Hemodialysis Clearance
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The clearance of a substance from the blood during a hemodialysis session.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Hemodialysis Clearance

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Hemodialysis Extraction Ratio
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The fractional content of a substance removed from the blood during a hemodialysis session.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Hemodialysis Extraction Ratio

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Half Tmax
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The midpoint time between dosing time and Tmax.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Half Tmax

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: K Slope of Distribution
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The distribution rate constant.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: K Slope of Distribution

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Lambda z
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The first order rate constant associated with the terminal (log-linear) portion of the curve.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Lambda Z

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Half-Life Lambda z
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: Terminal half-life.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Terminal Half Life

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Lambda z Lower Limit
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The lower limit on time for values to be included in the calculation of Lambda z.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Lambda Z Time Lower Limit

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Lambda z Lower Limit TAU
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The lower limit on time for values to be included in the calculation of Lambda z, calculated within a dosing interval.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Lambda z Lower Limit TAU

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Number of Points for Lambda z
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The number of time points used in computing Lambda z.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Sum of Lambda Z Timepoints

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Number of Points for Lambda z TAU
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The number of time points used in computing Lambda z determined in a dosing interval.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Number of Points for Lambda z TAU

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Lambda z Span
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The interval of time covered by the data points used in the terminal disposition phase regression analysis, divided by half life. This yields the terminal disposition phase duration expressed as the number of half lives.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Lambda Z Span

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Lambda z TAU
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The first order rate constant associated with the terminal (log-linear) portion of the curve, calculated within a dosing interval.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Lambda z TAU

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Lambda z Upper Limit
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The upper limit on time for values to be included in the calculation of Lambda z.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Lambda Z Time Upper Limit

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Lambda z Upper Limit TAU
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The upper limit on time for values to be included in the calculation of Lambda z, calculated within a dosing interval.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Lambda z Upper Limit TAU

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Mean Absorption Time
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: Mean absorption time of a substance administered by extravascular dosing.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Mean Absorption Time

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: MRT Extravasc Infinity Obs
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The mean residence time (MRT) extrapolated to infinity for a substance administered by extravascular dosing, calculated using the observed value of the last non-zero concentration. Extravascular MRT includes Mean Absorption Time (MAT).
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Mean Residence Time Infinity Observed by Extravascular Dose

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: MRT Extravasc Infinity Pred
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The mean residence time (MRT) extrapolated to infinity for a substance administered by extravascular dosing, calculated using the predicted value of the last non-zero concentration. Extravascular MRT includes Mean Absorption Time (MAT).
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Mean Residence Time Infinity Predicted by Extravascular Dose

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: MRT Extravasc to Last Nonzero Conc
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: Mean residence time (MRT) from the time of dosing to the time of the last measurable concentration for a substance administered by extravascular dosing. Extravascular MRT includes Mean Absorption Time (MAT).
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Mean Residence Time to Last Nonzero Concentration by Extravascular Dose

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: MRT IV Bolus Infinity Obs
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The mean residence time (MRT) extrapolated to infinity for a substance administered by intravascular bolus dosing, calculated using the observed value of the last non-zero concentration.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Mean Residence Time Infinity Observed by Intravascular Bolus Dose

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: MRT IV Bolus Infinity Pred
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The mean residence time (MRT) extrapolated to infinity for a substance administered by intravascular bolus dosing, calculated using the predicted value of the last non-zero concentration.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Mean Residence Time Infinity Predicted by Intravascular Bolus Dose

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: MRT IV Bolus to Last Nonzero Conc
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: Mean residence time (MRT) from the time of dosing to the time of the last measurable concentration, for a substance administered by intravascular bolus dosing.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Mean Residence Time to Last Nonzero Concentration by Intravascular Bolus Dose

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: MRT IV Cont Inf Infinity Obs
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The mean residence time (MRT) extrapolated to infinity for a substance administered by constant rate of continuous intravascular infusion, calculated using the observed value of the last non-zero concentration.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Mean Residence Time Intravenous Continuous Infusion Infinity Observed

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: MRT IV Cont Inf Infinity Pred
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The mean residence time (MRT) extrapolated to infinity for a substance administered by constant rate of continuous intravascular infusion, calculated using the predicted value of the last non-zero concentration.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Mean Residence Time Intravenous Continuous Infusion Infinity Predicted

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: MRT IV Cont Inf to Last Nonzero Conc
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: Mean residence time (MRT) from the time of dosing to the time of the last measurable concentration, for a substance administered by constant rate of continuous intravascular infusion.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Mean Residence Time Intravenous Continuous Infusion to Last Nonzero Concentration

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Nonrenal CL
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The total clearance of a substance from the blood less the renal clearance.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Nonrenal Clearance

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Nonrenal CL Norm by BMI
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The total clearance of a substance from the blood minus the renal clearance divided by the body mass index.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Nonrenal Clearance Normalized by BMI

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Nonrenal CL Norm by Dose
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The total clearance of a substance from the blood minus the renal clearance divided by the dose.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Nonrenal Clearance Normalized by Dose

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Nonrenal CL Norm by SA
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The total clearance of a substance from the blood minus the renal clearance divided by the surface area.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Nonrenal Clearance Normalized by SA

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Nonrenal CL Norm by WT
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The total clearance of a substance from the blood minus the renal clearance divided by the weight.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Nonrenal Clearance Normalized by WT

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Peak Trough Ratio
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The maximum concentration during a dosing interval divided by the concentration at the end of the dosing interval.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Peak Trough Ratio

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: R Squared
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The goodness of fit statistic for the terminal elimination phase.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: R Squared

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: R Squared Adjusted
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The goodness of fit statistic for the terminal elimination phase, adjusted for the number of time points used in the estimation of Lambda z.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Adjusted R Squared

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Ratio AUC
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The ratio of two AUC values.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Area Under the Curve Ratio

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Ratio AUC All
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The ratio of two AUC All values.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: AUC All Ratio

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Ratio AUC Infinity Obs
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The ratio of two AUC infinity observed values.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Area Under the Curve Ratio Infinity Observed

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Ratio AUC Infinity Pred
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The ratio of two AUC infinity predicted values.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Area Under the Curve Ratio Infinity Predicted

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Ratio AUC from T1 to T2 Norm by Dose
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The ratio of two AUC from T1 to T2 normalized by dose values.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Ratio AUC from T1 to T2 Normalized by Dose

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Ratio AUC from T1 to T2
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The ratio of two AUC from T1 to T2 values.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Ratio AUC From T1 to T2

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Ratio AUC Infinity Obs Norm by Dose
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The ratio of two AUC infinity observed normalized by dose values.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Ratio AUC Infinity Observed Normalized by Dose

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Ratio AUC to Last Nonzero Conc Norm by Dose
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The ratio of two AUC to last nonzero concentration normalized by dose values.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Ratio AUC to Last Nonzero Concentration Normalized by Dose

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Ratio AUC to Last Nonzero Conc
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The ratio of two AUC to last nonzero concentration values.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Ratio AUC to Last Nonzero Concentration

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Ratio AUC Over Dosing Interval
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The ratio of two AUCTAU values.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Ratio AUC Over Dosing Interval

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Ratio Average Concentration
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The ratio of two average concentration values.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Average Concentration Ratio

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Ratio CMAX
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The ratio of two Cmax values.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Cmax to Cmax Ratio Measurement

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Ratio Max Conc Norm by Dose
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The ratio of two maximum concentration normalized by dose values.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Ratio Maximum Concentration Normalized by Dose

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Ratio Min Conc
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The ratio of two cmin values.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Minimum Concentration Ratio

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Ratio Concentration
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The ratio of two concentration values.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Concentration Ratio

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Ratio Conc Trough
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The ratio of two CTROUGH values.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Ratio Concentration Trough

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Ratio of CMAX to CMIN
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The ratio of Cmax value to Cmin value.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Cmax to Cmin Ratio Measurement

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Ratio Amt Rec Infinity Obs
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The ratio of two amount recovered infinity observed values.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Ratio Amount Recovered Infinity Observed

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Ratio Amt Rec from T1 to T2
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The ratio of two amount recovered from T1 to T2 values.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Ratio Amount Recovered from T1 to T2

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Amt Rec Infinity Obs
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The cumulative amount recovered from the specimen type specified in PPSPEC extrapolated to infinity, calculated using the observed value of the last non-zero concentration.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Amount Recovered Infinity Observed

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Amt Rec Infinity Obs Norm by BMI
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The cumulative amount recovered from the specimen type specified in PPSPEC extrapolated to infinity, calculated using the observed value of the last non-zero concentration, divided by the body mass index.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Amount Recovered Infinity Observed Normalized by Body Mass Index

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Amt Rec Infinity Obs Norm by SA
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The cumulative amount recovered from the specimen type specified in PPSPEC extrapolated to infinity, calculated using the observed value of the last non-zero concentration, divided by the surface area.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Amount Recovered Infinity Observed Normalized by Surface Area

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Amt Rec Infinity Obs Norm by WT
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The cumulative amount recovered from the specimen type specified in PPSPEC extrapolated to infinity, calculated using the observed value of the last non-zero concentration, divided by the weight.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Amount Recovered Infinity Observed Normalized by Weight

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Amt Rec Infinity Pred
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The cumulative amount recovered from the specimen type specified in PPSPEC extrapolated to infinity, calculated using the predicted value of the last non-zero concentration.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Amount Recovered Infinity Predicted

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Amt Rec Infinity Pred Norm by BMI
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The cumulative amount recovered from the specimen type specified in PPSPEC extrapolated to infinity, calculated using the predicted value of the last non-zero concentration, divided by the body mass index.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Amount Recovered Infinity Predicted Normalized by Body Mass Index

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Amt Rec Infinity Pred Norm by SA
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The cumulative amount recovered from the specimen type specified in PPSPEC extrapolated to infinity, calculated using the predicted value of the last non-zero concentration, divided by the surface area.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Amount Recovered Infinity Predicted Normalized by Surface Area

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Amt Rec Infinity Pred Norm by WT
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The cumulative amount recovered from the specimen type specified in PPSPEC extrapolated to infinity, calculated using the predicted value of the last non-zero concentration, divided by the weight.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Amount Recovered Infinity Predicted Normalized by Weight

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Amt Rec from T1 to T2
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The cumulative amount recovered from the specimen type specified in PPSPEC over the interval from T1 to T2.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Amount Recovered from T1 to T2

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Amt Rec from T1 to T2 Norm by BMI
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The cumulative amount recovered from the specimen type specified in PPSPEC over the interval from T1 to T2 divided by body mass index.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Amount Recovered from T1 to T2 Normalized by Body Mass Index

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Amt Rec from T1 to T2 Norm by SA
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The cumulative amount recovered from the specimen type specified in PPSPEC over the interval from T1 to T2 divided by surface area.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Amount Recovered from T1 to T2 Normalized by Surface Area

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Amt Rec from T1 to T2 Norm by WT
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The cumulative amount recovered from the specimen type specified in PPSPEC over the interval from T1 to T2 divided by weight.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Amount Recovered from T1 to T2 Normalized by Weight

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Amt Rec to Last Nonzero Conc
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The cumulative amount recovered from the specimen type specified in PPSPEC, from the time of dosing to the last non-zero concentration.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Amount Recovered to Last Nonzero Concentration

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Amt Rec Over Dosing Interval
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The cumulative amount recovered from the specimen type specified in PPSPEC between doses (TAU).
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Amount Recovered Over Dosing Interval

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Amt Rec Over Dosing Interval Norm by BMI
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The cumulative amount recovered from the specimen type specified in PPSPEC between doses (TAU) divided by body mass index.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Amount Recovered Over Dosing Interval Normalized by Body Mass Index

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Amt Rec Over Dosing Interval Norm by SA
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The cumulative amount recovered from the specimen type specified in PPSPEC between doses (TAU) divided by surface area.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Amount Recovered Over Dosing Interval Normalized by Surface Area

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Amt Rec Over Dosing Interval Norm by WT
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The cumulative amount recovered from the specimen type specified in PPSPEC between doses (TAU) divided by weight.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Amount Recovered Over Dosing Interval Normalized by Weight

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Pct Rec Infinity Obs
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The percentage of the administered dose that is recovered from the specimen type specified in PPSPEC extrapolated to infinity, calculated using the observed value of the last non-zero concentration.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Percent Recovered Infinity Observed

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Pct Rec Infinity Obs Norm by BMI
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The percentage of the administered dose that is recovered from the specimen type specified in PPSPEC extrapolated to infinity, calculated using the observed value of the last non-zero concentration, divided by the body mass index.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Percent Recovered Infinity Observed Normalized by Body Mass Index

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Pct Rec Infinity Obs Norm by SA
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The percentage of the administered dose that is recovered from the specimen type specified in PPSPEC extrapolated to infinity, calculated using the observed value of the last non-zero concentration, divided by the surface area.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Percent Recovered Infinity Observed Normalized by Surface Area

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Pct Rec Infinity Obs Norm by WT
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The percentage of the administered dose that is recovered from the specimen type specified in PPSPEC extrapolated to infinity, calculated using the observed value of the last non-zero concentration, divided by the weight.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Percent Recovered Infinity Observed Normalized by Weight

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Pct Rec Infinity Pred
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The percentage of the administered dose that is recovered from the specimen type specified in PPSPEC extrapolated to infinity, calculated using the predicted value of the last non-zero concentration.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Percent Recovered Infinity Predicted

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Pct Rec Infinity Pred Norm by BMI
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The percentage of the administered dose that is recovered from the specimen type specified in PPSPEC extrapolated to infinity, calculated using the predicted value of the last non-zero concentration, divided by the body mass index.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Percent Recovered Infinity Predicted Normalized by Body Mass Index

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Pct Rec Infinity Pred Norm by SA
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The percentage of the administered dose that is recovered from the specimen type specified in PPSPEC extrapolated to infinity, calculated using the predicted value of the last non-zero concentration, divided by the surface area.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Percent Recovered Infinity Predicted Normalized by Surface Area

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Pct Rec Infinity Pred Norm by WT
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The percentage of the administered dose that is recovered from the specimen type specified in PPSPEC extrapolated to infinity, calculated using the predicted value of the last non-zero concentration, divided by the weight.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Percent Recovered Infinity Predicted Normalized by Weight

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Pct Rec from T1 to T2
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The percentage of the administered dose that is recovered from the specimen type specified in PPSPEC, over the interval between T1 and T2.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Percent Recovered from T1 to T2

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Pct Rec from T1 to T2 Norm by BMI
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The percentage of the administered dose that is recovered from the specimen type specified in PPSPEC, over the interval between T1 and T2 divided by body mass index.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Percent Recovered from T1 to T2 Normalized by Body Mass Index

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Pct Rec from T1 to T2 Norm by SA
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The percentage of the administered dose that is recovered from the specimen type specified in PPSPEC, over the interval between T1 and T2 divided by surface area.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Percent Recovered from T1 to T2 Normalized by Surface Area

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Pct Rec from T1 to T2 Norm by WT
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The percentage of the administered dose that is recovered from the specimen type specified in PPSPEC, over the interval between T1 and T2 divided by weight.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Percent Recovered from T1 to T2 Normalized by Weight

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Pct Rec to Last Nonzero Conc
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The percentage of the administered dose that is recovered from the specimen type specified in PPSPEC, from the time of dosing to the last non-zero concentration.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Percent Recovered To Last Nonzero Concentration

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Pct Rec Over Dosing Interval
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The percentage of the administered dose that is recovered from the specimen type specified in PPSPEC, between doses (TAU).
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Percent Recovered Over Dosing Interval

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Pct Rec Over Dosing Interval Norm by BMI
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The percentage of the administered dose that is recovered from the specimen type specified in PPSPEC, between doses (TAU) divided by the body mass index.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Percent Recovered Over Dosing Interval Normalized by Body Mass Index

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Pct Rec Over Dosing Interval Norm by SA
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The percentage of the administered dose that is recovered from the specimen type specified in PPSPEC, between doses (TAU) divided by surface area.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Percent Recovered Over Dosing Interval Normalized by Surface Area

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Pct Rec Over Dosing Interval Norm by WT
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The percentage of the administered dose that is recovered from the specimen type specified in PPSPEC, between doses (TAU) divided by weight.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Percent Recovered Over Dosing Interval Normalized by Weight

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Renal CL
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The clearance of a substance from the blood by the kidneys.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Renal Clearance

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Renal CL Norm by BMI
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The clearance of a substance from the blood by the kidneys divided by the body mass index.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Renal Clearance Normalized by BMI

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Renal CL Norm by Dose
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The clearance of a substance from the blood by the kidneys divided by the dose.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Renal Clearance Normalized by Dose

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Renal CL Norm by SA
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The clearance of a substance from the blood by the kidneys divided by the surface area.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Renal Clearance Normalized by SA

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Renal CL Norm by WT
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The clearance of a substance from the blood by the kidneys divided by the weight.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Renal Clearance Normalized by WT

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Renal CL for Dose Int
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The clearance of a substance from the blood by the kidneys, calculated using AUCTAU.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Renal Clearance for Dose Interval

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Renal CL from T1 to T2
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The clearance of a substance from the blood by the kidneys over the interval from T1 to T2.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Renal Clearance from T1 to T2

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Renal CL from T1 to T2 Norm by BMI
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The clearance of a substance from the blood by the kidneys over the interval from T1 to T2 divided by the body mass index.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Renal Clearance from T1 to T2 Normalized by Body Mass Index

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Renal CL from T1 to T2 Norm by Dose
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The clearance of a substance from the blood by the kidneys over the interval from T1 to T2 divided by the dose.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Renal Clearance from T1 to T2 Normalized by Dose

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Renal CL from T1 to T2 Norm by SA
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The clearance of a substance from the blood by the kidneys over the interval from T1 to T2 divided by the surface area.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Renal Clearance from T1 to T2 Normalized by Surface Area

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Renal CL from T1 to T2 Norm by WT
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The clearance of a substance from the blood by the kidneys over the interval from T1 to T2 divided by the weight.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Renal Clearance from T1 to T2 Normalized by Weight

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Renal CL for Dose Int Norm by BMI
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The clearance of a substance from the blood by the kidneys, calculated using AUCTAU, divided by the body mass index.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Renal Clearance for Dose Interval Normalized by Body Mass Index

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Renal CL for Dose Int Norm by Dose
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The clearance of a substance from the blood by the kidneys, calculated using AUCTAU, divided by the dose.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Renal Clearance for Dose Interval Normalized by Dose

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Renal CL for Dose Int Norm by SA
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The clearance of a substance from the blood by the kidneys, calculated using AUCTAU, divided by the surface area.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Renal Clearance for Dose Interval Normalized by Surface Area

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Renal CL for Dose Int Norm by WT
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The clearance of a substance from the blood by the kidneys, calculated using AUCTAU, divided by the weight.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Renal Clearance for Dose Interval Normalized by Weight

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Renal CL for Unbound Drug
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The unbound fraction of drug within the portion of total clearance attributed to the kidneys.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Renal Clearance for Unbound Drug

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Stationarity Ratio AUC
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The area under the curve (AUCTAU) at steady state divided by the area under the curve extrapolated to infinity for the initial dosing interval.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Stationarity Ratio Area Under the Curve

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Swing
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The difference between Cmax and Cmin standardized to Cmin within a dosing interval.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: PK Swing

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Dosing Interval
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The duration of time between two doses.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Dosing Interval

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Half-Life TAU
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: Half-life calculated within a dosing interval.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Half-Life TAU

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Time Until First Nonzero Conc
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The time prior to the first measurable (non-zero) concentration.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Time until First Nonzero Concentration

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Time of Last Nonzero Conc
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The time of the last measurable (positive) concentration.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Time of Last Nonzero Concentration

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Time of CMAX
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The time of maximum observed concentration sampled during a dosing interval.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Tmax

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Time of CMIN Observation
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The time of minimum concentration sampled during a dosing interval.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Tmin

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Trough Peak Ratio
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The concentration at the start of a dosing interval divided by the maximum concentration during the dosing interval.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Trough Peak Ratio

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Vol Dist Initial
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The initial volume of distribution for a substance administered by bolus intravascular dosing.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Initial Volume of Distribution

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Vol Dist Initial Norm by BMI
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The initial volume of distribution for a substance administered by bolus intravascular dosing divided by the body mass index.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Initial Volume of Distribution Normalized by Body Mass Index

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Vol Dist Initial Norm by Dose
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The initial volume of distribution for a substance administered by bolus intravascular dosing divided by the dose.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Initial Volume of Distribution Normalized by Dose

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Vol Dist Initial Norm by SA
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The initial volume of distribution for a substance administered by bolus intravascular dosing divided by the surface area.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Initial Volume of Distribution Normalized by Surface Area

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Vol Dist Initial Norm by WT
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The initial volume of distribution for a substance administered by bolus intravascular dosing divided by the weight.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Initial Volume of Distribution Normalized by Weight

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Sum of Urine Vol
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The sum of urine volumes that are used for PK parameters.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Sum Urine Volume

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Vol Dist Steady State Obs
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The volume of distribution at steady state based on the observed CLST for a substance administered by intravascular dosing.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Observed Steady State Volume of Distribution

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Vol Dist Steady State Obs Norm by BMI
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The volume of distribution at steady state based on the observed CLST for a substance administered by intravascular dosing divided by the body mass index.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Observed Steady State Volume of Distribution Normalized by Body Mass Index

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Vol Dist Steady State Obs by B
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The volume of distribution at steady state based on the observed CLST for a substance administered, divided by the fraction of bound drug.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Volume of Distribution Steady State Observed by Bound Drug

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Vol Dist Steady State Obs Norm by Dose
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The volume of distribution at steady state based on the observed CLST for a substance administered by intravascular dosing divided by the dose.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Observed Steady State Volume of Distribution Normalized by Dose

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Vol Dist Steady State Obs by F
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The volume of distribution at steady state based on the observed CLST for a substance administered by extravascular dosing, divided by the fraction of dose absorbed.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Volume of Distribution Steady State Observed by Fraction of Dose Absorbed

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Vol Dist Steady State Obs Norm by SA
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The volume of distribution at steady state based on the observed CLST for a substance administered by intravascular dosing divided by the surface area.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Observed Steady State Volume of Distribution Normalized by Surface Area

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Vol Dist Steady State Obs by UB
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The volume of distribution at steady state based on the observed CLST for a substance administered, divided by the fraction of unbound drug.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Volume of Distribution Steady State Observed by Unbound Drug

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Vol Dist Steady State Obs Norm by WT
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The volume of distribution at steady state based on the observed CLST for a substance administered by intravascular dosing divided by the weight.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Observed Steady State Volume of Distribution Normalized by Weight

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Vol Dist Steady State Pred
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The volume of distribution at steady state based on the predicted CLST for a substance administered by intravascular dosing.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Predicted Steady State Volume of Distribution

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Vol Dist Steady State Pred Norm by BMI
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The volume of distribution at steady state based on the predicted CLST for a substance administered by intravascular dosing divided by the body mass index.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Predicted Steady State Volume of Distribution Normalized by Body Mass Index

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Vol Dist Steady State Pred by B
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The volume of distribution at steady state based on the predicted CLST for a substance administered, divided by the fraction of bound drug.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Volume of Distribution Steady State Predicted by Bound Drug

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Vol Dist Steady State Pred Norm by Dose
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The volume of distribution at steady state based on the predicted CLST for a substance administered by intravascular dosing divided by the dose.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Predicted Steady State Volume of Distribution Normalized by Dose

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Vol Dist Steady State Pred by F
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The volume of distribution at steady state based on the predicted CLST for a substance administered by extravascular dosing, divided by the fraction of dose absorbed.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Volume of Distribution Steady State Predicted by Fraction of Dose Absorbed

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Vol Dist Steady State Pred Norm by SA
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The volume of distribution at steady state based on the predicted CLST for a substance administered by intravascular dosing divided by the surface area.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Predicted Steady State Volume of Distribution Normalized by Surface Area

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Vol Dist Steady State Pred by UB

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Vol Dist Steady State Pred Norm by WT
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The volume of distribution at steady state based on the predicted CLST for a substance administered by intravascular dosing divided by the weight.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Predicted Steady State Volume of Distribution Normalized by Weight

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Vz Obs by F
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The volume of distribution associated with the terminal slope following extravascular administration divided by the fraction of dose absorbed, calculated using the observed value of the last non-zero concentration.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Observed Volume of Distribution of Absorbed Fraction

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Vz Obs by F Norm by BMI
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The volume of distribution associated with the terminal slope following extravascular administration divided by the fraction of dose absorbed, calculated using the observed value of the last non-zero concentration, divided by the body mass index.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Volume of Distribution of Fraction Dose Observed Normalized by Body Mass Index

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Vz Obs by F Norm by Dose
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The volume of distribution associated with the terminal slope following extravascular administration divided by the fraction of dose absorbed, calculated using the observed value of the last non-zero concentration, divided by the dose.
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Volume of Distribution of Fraction Dose Observed Normalized by Dose

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Vz Obs by F Norm by SA
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The volume of distribution associated with the terminal slope following extravascular administration divided by the fraction of dose absorbed, calculated using the observed value of the last non-zero concentration, divided by the surface area.
